<title>William Maxwell's Black Characters in Billie Dyer and Other Stories</title>
<meta name="keywords" content="William Maxwell; blacks; John A. Ross; Hattie Dyer Brummell; Hattie Dyer; Billie Dyer; Lincoln, Illinois; Leigh Henson; Debbie Ross; Lincoln, IL">
<meta name="description" content="This essay examines Maxwell's research on the Dyer-Brummell families, describes my own corresponding research, analyzes Maxwell's portrayal of blacks in his final stories, and draws some conclusions about his literary art.">
