		Exemplary Faculty of Lincoln College at Mid-Twentieth Century</font></a></font></b></p>
		<p align="center"><b><font color="#008000" face="Arial" size="2">
		<a target="_blank" href="http://findinglincolnillinois.com/krotzes.html">
		<font color="#008000">A Tribute to the Krotzes of Lincoln, Illinois</font></a></font></b></p>
		<p align="center"><font color="#008000" face="Arial" size="2"><b>
		<a target="_blank" href="http://findinglincolnillinois.com/authorrobertwilson.html">
		<font color="#008000">A Tribute to Robert Wilson (LCHS '46): Author of
		<i>Young in Illinois</i>, Movies Editor of <i>December </i>Magazine, 
		Friend and Colleague of December Press Publisher Curt Johnson, and 
		Correspondent with William Maxwell</font></a></b></font></p>
		<p align="center"><font color="#008000" face="Arial" size="2"><b>
		<font color="#008000">
		<a target="_blank" href="http://www.braddye.com/lincoln.html">
		<font color="#008000">Brad Dye (LCHS '60): His Lincoln, Illinois, Web 
		Site</font></a></font></b><a target="_blank" href="http://www.braddye.com/lincoln.html"><font color="#008000">,
		</font></a><br>
		including photos of many churches</font></p>
		<p><b><font color="#008000" face="Arial" size="2">
		<a target="_blank" href="http://findinglincolnillinois.com/davearmbrust.html">
		<font color="#008000">Dave Armbrust's Memorabilia of Lincoln, Illinois</font></a></font></b></p>
		<p align="center"><b><font color="#008000" face="Arial" size="2">
		<a target="_blank" href="http://findinglincolnillinois.com/fikuarts.html">
		<font color="#008000">J. Richard <br>
		(JR) Fikuart <br>
		(LCHS '65): <br>
		T</font></a></font></b><font color="#008000" face="Arial" size="2"><b><font color="#008000"><a target="_blank" href="http://findinglincolnillinois.com/fikuarts.html"><font color="#008000">he 
		Fikuarts of Lincoln, Illinois</font></a>,</font> </b>including their 
		connections to the William Maxwell family and three generations of 
		family fun at Lincoln Lakes</font></p>
		<p align="center"><b><font color="#008000" face="Arial" size="2">
		<a target="_blank" href="http://findinglincolnillinois.com/lchsclassof1960/autobios/jgibson.html">
