		Grandmother Lena &amp; Her West Side Tavern on Sangamon Street in the Route 
		66 Era</font></a></b></font></p>
		<p align="center"><font color="#008000" face="Arial" size="2"><b>
		<a target="_blank" href="http://findinglincolnillinois.com/knecht/jknecht.html">
