		(LCHS '62): Memoir and Short Story, &quot;Other People's Money,&quot; Set in 
		Hickey's Billiards on Chicago Street in the Route 66 Era</font></a></b></font></p>
		<p align="center"><font color="#008000" face="Arial" size="2"><b>
		<a target="_blank" href="http://findinglincolnillinois.com/contributors/williamakrueger.html">
