		for His Books About Murders in Lincoln</font></a></b></font></p>
		<p align="center"><b><font color="#008000" face="Arial" size="2">
		<a target="_blank" href="http://findinglincolnillinois.com/lchsclassof1960/autobios/nschroeder.htm">
